# Student Portfolio Website

A personal portfolio website designed to showcase my skills, projects, certifications, and achievements as a Computer Science student. This website serves as my digital portfolio and helps recruiters, mentors, and peers learn more about my work and interests.

## Features

- Responsive design for desktop and mobile devices
- Professional homepage with introduction
- About Me section
- Skills showcase
- Projects gallery
- Certifications and achievements
- Contact information
- Modern and user-friendly interface

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Project Structure

├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
├── images/
└── README.md

